fields.value: The Association Between Adjustment and Self-Insight into Emotional and Cognitive Abilities Stage 1 and 2 Documents

authorAffiliation.value: Rotman School of Management, University of Toronto

datasetContactAffiliation.value: Rotman School of Management, University of Toronto

dsDescriptionValue.value: This is the complete set of documents (manuscript, supplementary materials, pilot data and materials, and analysis code) for our registered report proposal (Stage 1 and 2) on self-insight into cognitive and emotional abilities. This version contains the most up to date version of the documents. To download the csv versions of the data that are required by the code, researchers need to select the “Original File Format (Comma Separated Values)” option under “Download.” The code for analysis will not work if researchers download the tab versions of the data files instead.
